Steve,



At the risk of starting a big critical string of posts

you forget that you and I experienced the negative side of this research

together and you even went as far as to do a cleansing ritual involving a medium.



And have told me on numerous occasions that you do a protection ritual before every session.

All I can say is that if you where not being truthful, that is why you experienced the negative 

incidents that plagued your home and your research. 



Please, and I&#39;m asking nicely do not take the road of hypocrisy just to disagree with me.

It would not be fare to the new individuals that may trust your opinion.



I do not try or presume to tell anyone one what they do or do not have to do, and if I

present my opinion that way I apologize to all. I only try to offer my experienced opinion as you do.



Steve, lets not start these insinuating posts back and forth, lets remain civil and friendly for the 

sake of the research.



And to any and all that read this post the protection ritual is just another diverse tool in our research

tool box, there to use if you personally feel it&#39;s necessary.



Steve and I have taken different paths as far as research ideas are concerned and felt it would be

more beneficial to us both and to the research on a whole if we pursued individual avenues of research as apposed 

to a research collaboration.

If some of the ripples from this have reached this forum I for one apologise and will do my best to keep my posts to a civil

and professional level.



Bruce








Bruce Halliday 







