couple problems here personally. I guess for people who believe in 
it i guess it couldn&#39;t hurt, as for my problems i can&#39;t say it was 
from not doing a protection prayer but i also can&#39;t say it was. 
Another paranormal toss up for each researcher to decide i guess. 
That&#39;s why i never tell anyone what to do, there is no right and 
wrong way to do anything in this field. People just have to draw 
conclusions on their own and get results in the way that they seem 
fit. And than report, and not tell people for a fact that it should 
be done that way. Each person with their own ideas will eventually 
put all the pieces to this paranormal puzzle together.

-Steve H.

